OL,3,CArsenal fans line streets of north
OL,4,CLondon for Premier League trophy parade
OL,6,FThousands of Arsenal fans have lined
OL,7,Fthe streets of north London for the
OL,8,Fclub's Premier League victory parade
OL,9,Falong a 5.6-mile route through the
OL,10,FGunners' heartlands.
OL,12,FArsenal will attempt to put their
OL,13,FEuropean pain to one side with the
OL,14,Fopen-top bus parade that marks their
OL,15,Ffirst Premier League title since 2004.
OL,17,FMikel Arteta's title-winning team are
OL,18,Fdue to set off at 2pm ` just 18 hours
OL,19,Fafter their Champions League
OL,20,Fheartbreak against Paris St Germain in
OL,21,FBudapest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
