OL,3,CArsenal fans line streets of north
OL,4,CLondon for Premier League trophy parade
OL,6,FAs many as half-a-million Arsenal
OL,7,Fsupporters are expected to line the
OL,8,Fstreets for the parade which is
OL,9,Fexpected to last two hours.
OL,11,FThe Gunners had been hoping for a
OL,12,Fdouble celebration by following up
OL,13,Ftheir league success with a first
OL,14,FChampions League trophy in the club's
OL,15,F140-year history.
OL,17,FHowever, Eberechi Eze and Gabriel both
OL,18,Fmissed their penalties in Saturday's
OL,19,Fnerve-jangling shootout to allow PSG
OL,20,Fto retain their crown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
